help for gifted parents kathy matthews offers no-nonsense advice with a sense of humor . this how-to-parent-and-feel-good-about-yourself book is a must read . . .and , along with jim trelease 's book on reading aloud to your children , will certainly become a standard baby shower gift from me in the coming years . matthews speaks with the authority of a mother comfortable in her own skin -- and with her own children . brava , ms. matthews